It seems that `move_only_holder_caster` is not aggressive enough when calling `get()`:
https://github.com/pybind/pybind11/blob/86e2ad4f77442c3350f9a2476650da6bee253c52/include/pybind11/cast.h#L1460-L1463
https://github.com/pybind/pybind11/blob/86e2ad4f77442c3350f9a2476650da6bee253c52/include/pybind11/cast.h#L1369-L1372

I believe the simple solution would be to teach `holder_helper<holder_type>::get(src)` to use `release()` for `T&&` when `T = unique_ptr<U, ...>`.

